<li id="cite_note-Klein-23">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Klein_23-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Klein_23-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Klein_23-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> Disorders of the Self by <a href="/wiki/James_F._Masterson" title="James F. Masterson">James F. Masterson</a> and Ralph Klein 1995 subheading 'Secret Pure Schizoid Cluster Disorder' pp 25-27. Klein was Clinical Director of the Masterson Institute and Assistant Professor of Psychiatry at the Columbia University College of Physicians and Surgeons, New York</li>
